msgid "Query the audit log of all admin actions. Every state-changing admin command is automatically recorded with timestamp, actor, action, and target."
msgstr "查詢所有管理行動的審計日誌。 每一個改變狀態的管理員命令都會自動記錄時間戳,演員,動作,和目標."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/cmd_knock.html.heex:36
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Rate limited: once per 60 seconds per channel"
msgstr "限速率:每頻道每60秒一次"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/cmd_alias.html.heex:56
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Recursive aliases (A calls B calls A) are detected and rejected (max 5 levels)"
msgstr "遞歸別名(A calls B calls A)被檢測和拒絕(最大5級)"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/cmd_ns.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Register and protect your nickname with a password through NickServ, the nickname services bot. Once registered, nobody else can use your name."
msgstr "通過暱稱服務機器人NickServe的密碼註冊並保護您的暱稱. 一旦註冊, 沒有人可以使用你的名字。"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/cmd_autojoin.html.heex:34
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Registered users only — guests cannot save auto-join lists"
msgstr "只有註冊用戶——客人不能保存自動連接列表"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/cmd_autorespond.html.heex:39
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Registered users only — rules are persisted across sessions"
msgstr "僅登記用戶——各屆均堅持規則"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/cmd_alias.html.heex:68
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Registered users: aliases are saved across sessions. Guests: session-only"
msgstr "註冊用戶:在會話中保存別名. 來賓:只開會"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/cmd_bio.html.heex:31
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Registered users: bio is saved across sessions"
msgstr "註冊用戶:在會話中保存生物"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/cmd_popups.html.heex:23
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Registered users: custom menus are saved across sessions"
msgstr "註冊用戶:自定義菜單在會話中保存"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/cmd_notify.html.heex:29
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Registered users: list is saved across sessions"
msgstr "註冊用戶: 列表保存到會話中"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/cmd_singleplayer.html.heex:16
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Regular users should join"
msgstr "常規用戶應加入"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/cmd_unban.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Remove a ban from a user, allowing them to rejoin the channel."
msgstr "從用戶中刪除一個禁止,讓他們重新加入頻道."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/cmd_unmute.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Remove a channel mute from a user, allowing them to send messages again."
msgstr "從用戶中刪除一個頻道啞音, 允許他們再次發送消息 。"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/cmd_kick.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Remove a user from the channel. Unlike"
msgstr "從頻道中刪除一個用戶。 與"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/cmd_deop.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Remove operator status from a user in the current channel. This is a shorthand for"
msgstr "從當前頻道的用戶中刪除操作員狀態 。 這是簡寫"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/cmd_clearmotd.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Remove the server's Message of the Day so that new users connecting won't see any MOTD."
msgstr "刪除服務器的每日信件, 這樣連接的新用戶不會看到任何 MOTD 。"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/cmd_clearwelcome.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Remove the welcome message from the current channel so that new users joining won't see one."
msgstr "從當前頻道刪除歡迎消息, 這樣新用戶不會看到一個 。"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/cmd_devoice.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Remove voice status from a user in the current channel. This is a shorthand for"
msgstr "從當前頻道的用戶中刪除語音狀態 。 這是簡寫"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/cmd_clear.html.heex:11
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Removes all visible messages from whichever window you're currently viewing — a channel, a PM conversation, or the Status tab. This only affects your screen; other users' windows are not changed. The messages are gone permanently and cannot be recovered by scrolling up."
msgstr "從您目前查看的窗口中移除所有可見消息——一個頻道,一個PM對話,或者狀態標籤. 這隻影響您的屏幕; 其他用戶的窗口沒有更改 。 信件已永久消失, 無法通過滾動回收 。"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/cmd_unban.html.heex:10
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Removes the ban entry for the specified user. Once unbanned, the user can rejoin the channel normally. For registered channels, the unban is persisted. You can also unban using"
msgstr "刪除指定用戶的禁止項。 一旦解除封禁,用戶可以正常地重新加入頻道. 對於已註冊的渠道,繼續實行禁令。 您還可以取消禁用"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/cmd_unignore.html.heex:13
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Removes the user from your ignore list. Their messages, PMs, actions, and invites (whichever were being blocked) will be visible again immediately. To see who you're currently ignoring, run"
msgstr "從忽略列表中刪除用戶。 他們的訊息、首相、行動、邀請(無論何時被封殺), 看看你現在忽略了誰,快跑"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/cmd_timer.html.heex:45
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Repeating: 10 to 86,400 seconds minimum interval"
msgstr "重複: 10至86 400秒最小間隔"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/cmd_knock.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Request to be let into an invite-only (+i) channel. Channel operators see your knock and can choose to invite you in."
msgstr "請求被允許進入只邀請的(+i)頻道. 頻道操作員看到你的敲門,可以選擇邀請你進來."

