#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Send a message to all users who have opted in to receive operator announcements by enabling +w user mode."
msgstr "向所有選擇通過啓用 +w 用戶模式接收操作員通知的用戶發送消息 。"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/cmd_msg.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Send a private message to another user. This opens a PM conversation tab for both of you."
msgstr "向另一個用戶發送私人消息 。 這爲你們倆打開了首相談話的標籤"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/cmd_me.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Send an action message that describes what you're doing. It appears to everyone in the channel as"
msgstr "發送一個動作信息 描述你在做什麼。 頻道里的每個人都覺得"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/cmd_announce.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Send an urgent broadcast message to every connected user. This is for critical server-wide announcements that everyone must see."
msgstr "向每個連接的用戶發送緊急廣播信息. 這是爲大家必須看到的關鍵的全服務器公告。"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/cmd_admin.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Server administration commands for managing users, channels, services, and settings. Only available to server administrators and operators."
msgstr "管理用戶、頻道、服務和設置的服務器管理命令。 僅供服務器管理員和操作員使用."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/cmd_clearmotd.html.heex:18
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/cmd_setmotd.html.heex:20
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Server administrator only"
msgstr "只有服務器管理員"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/cmd_announce.html.heex:26
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Server administrator only — regular users cannot send announcements"
msgstr "只有服務器管理員——普通用戶不能發送通知"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/cmd_admin_debug.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Server debug tools for viewing runtime information about the BEAM VM. Requires server administrator role. Read-only, no side effects."
msgstr "用於查看BEAM VM運行時信息的服務器調試工具. 需要服務器管理員角色 。 只讀,沒有副作用."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/cmd_wallops.html.heex:30
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Server operator or administrator only"
msgstr "僅限服務器操作員或管理員"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/cmd_game.html.heex:28
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Sessions expire after 5 minutes if the peer doesn't join"
msgstr "如果對等方不加入, 會話在5分鐘後到期"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/cmd_setwelcome.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Set a message shown once to each user when they join the current channel. Great for posting rules or helpful information for newcomers."
msgstr "設定每個用戶加入當前頻道時顯示一次的消息 。 給新來者張貼規則或有用信息真好。"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/cmd_bio.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Set a short \"about me\" text that appears when others look you up with"
msgstr "設置一個簡短的“關於我”的文本,當別人在查你時出現"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/cmd_autojoin.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Set channels to join automatically every time you connect, so you never have to manually rejoin your favorite rooms."
msgstr "設置頻道,每次連接時自動加入,所以你不必手動重新加入你最喜歡的房間."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/cmd_setmotd.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Set the server's Message of the Day — a welcome message shown to all users when they connect."
msgstr "設置服務器的當日信件——當所有用戶連接時向它們顯示的歡迎信件."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/cmd_perform.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Set up commands that automatically run every time you connect, like identifying with NickServ or joining channels."
msgstr "設置每次連接時自動運行的命令,例如識別與NickServ或加入頻道."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/cmd_setmotd.html.heex:13
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Sets or replaces the server MOTD. After setting it, all newly connecting users will see this message in the Status tab when they join. Existing connected users are not notified — only new connections see the MOTD. Any previous MOTD is replaced."
msgstr "設置或替換服務器MOTD. 設置後, 所有新連接的用戶加入時都會在狀態標籤中看到此消息 。 現有連接的用戶沒有被通知——只有新連接看到MOTD. 任何先前的MOTD都被替換."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/cmd_whowas.html.heex:13
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Shows information about a user who has disconnected within the configured retention period: their last seen time, which channels they were in, and their quit message (if they provided one). This is useful when you notice someone has left and want to know when and why. Lookups are case-insensitive. If no record exists, a \"no whowas information available\" message is shown."
msgstr "顯示一個用戶在配置的保留期內斷開連接的信息:他們最後一次看到的時間,他們所在的頻道,以及他們的退出消息(如果他們提供了的話). 當你注意到有人離開 想知道時間和原因時,這是有用的。 檢查是忽略大小寫。 如果沒有記錄,則會顯示“沒有信息可用”。"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/cmd_singleplayer.html.heex:27
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Solo Arcade"
msgstr "獨角街"

